I think eventually, you know, you do get more confident, right, as you do more. So you obviously encourage yourself to do more as well.

00:58:15.560 --> 00:58:25.560
Right. But from Wales, I think one of the scariest things I've had to do is go to the Eisteddfod. So this is a national pageant and as a child, you have to do it.

00:58:25.560 --> 00:58:37.560
